Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Carter boosts arms budget
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043w0yh
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 13 Jan 1980
Carter changes liberal policy re arms spending following Russian invasion of Afghanistan. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less